    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with character? This well-loved ride is ready for its next chapter! It's in honest, fair condition, showing some expected wear and tear for its age, but it still runs reliably and gets the job done. If you're looking for a solid value that you can drive away today without any surprises, this is the one for you!",
