      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail has been meticulously maintained to preserve its original factory luster. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a masterpiece of automotive engineering that shows virtually no signs of wear.",
      "price": 48500.0,
